quran[88]{c,v,t}:
  38,1,"Ṣaad, m wẽen ne Alkʋrãanã sẽn yaa tẽegrã, (ɑd yellã pɑ wɑ kɩfɩr-dãmbã sẽn tẽed tɩ lɑgm-n-tɑɑse n be ne Wẽndɑ ye)."
  38,2,"Pa woto ye! Sẽn kɩfl-bã bee waoog-m-meng la yõs-taab pʋga."
  38,3,"Zamaan-rãmb sõor waoog Tõnd sẽn halk sẽn reng bãmb taoore, tɩ b moon n boole, la pa le yɑɑ põsg wakat ye."
  38,4,"La b (Mak-rãmba) maan yel-solemd ne bugsd sẽn n wa bãmb nengẽ, n yi bãmb pʋgẽ, tɩ kɩfr-dãmba yeele: ""yãoã yaa tɩɩm soaba, n ya pʋyagda"","
  38,5,"A maana soaben-dãmbã tɩ lebg soab a yembre? Ad yãoã yaa yell sẽn yaa yel-solemd tεkẽ""."
  38,6,"Tɩ b zu-raadã yi n yeele: ""kell-y n kẽng bala, la y maan sugr ne y soaben-rãmbã, ad yãoã yaa yell b sẽn rat n yõk yãmb ne-a n wilyã,"
  38,7,"Tõnd pa wʋm yãoondã diin-rãmbɑ tɑɑbã pʋgẽ ye, yãoã yaa yel-nangdɩ"","
  38,8,"Yẽ zug la b sik tẽegrã (Alkʋrãaa) tõnd sʋka?"" Pa woto ye, b bee sãmbs pʋgẽ ne Mam tẽegrã. Pa woto ye, b na n pa lemb Mam naongã ye."
  38,9,"Bɩ fo Soabã yoslgã baoã bee bãmb nengẽ, sẽn yaa wilb Naabã, n yaa kõtã?."
  38,10,"Bɩ bãmb soo saas la tẽng naam la bũmb ning sẽn be bãmb b yiibã sʋkã? Bɩ b rʋ a nengẽ ne b sẽn tõe sor ning fãa."
  38,11,"Bambã yaa tãp sẽn kong pãngɑ wɑlɑ sulã-rãmbã sẽn reng tɑoor n kɩɩsã sẽn kong pãng tɩ b tõogbã."
  38,12,"Taoor tɩ bãmb nan pa wa, a Nuuh nebã la a Aad, la a Fîr-Aoon sẽn yaa bayã soabã yagsame."
  38,13,"La a Samuud, la a Lʋʋt nebã, la tɩɩsã rãmb (A sʋ'ayb nebã) me yagsame, bãmbã la sula rãmba,"
  38,14,"Bãmb yembr fãa pa yɩ rẽndame t'a yagsa tẽn-tʋʋmbã, tɩ Mam naongã sɩdg b zugu."
  38,15,"La bãmbã rãmbã pa gʋʋdi, ralla kaas-vuk bala, sẽn pa tar yɩlenga."
  38,16,"La b yeel yã: ""yaa tõnd Soaba! kõ tõnd d pʋɩɩrã tao-tao tɩ Geelgã Raar nan pa ta ye""."
  38,17,"Maan sugr ne b sẽn yetã, la f tẽeg Tõnd yamb a Dawʋʋd sẽn ya pãngã soabã, ad a yaa lebs-m-meng soaba."
  38,18,"Tõnd noma tãmsã tɩ b lagem-a n yɩlgd Wẽnd zaabr la yibeoogo."
  38,19,"Tɩ liuuli wã yaa sẽn tigmi, b fãa gill yaa sẽn lebs b mens Wẽnd nengẽ n pʋgd a Dawʋʋda."
  38,20,"La Tõnd kenga a naamã, la D kõ-a bʋʋd-minim la goam welgre."
  38,21,"La zabd-n-taasã kɩbar waa fo nengẽ bɩ? Wakat ning b sẽn wa n kal ɑ tũudmã zĩig lalgã n kẽ wã."
  38,22,"N kẽ a Dawʋʋd nengẽ, t'a yaeese, tɩ b yeele: ""ra yaees ye, tõnd yaa zabd-n-taas a yiibu, tõnd ned ɑ yembr n wẽg a to. Bɩ f bʋ tõnd sʋk ne sɩd la f ra maan n zʋʋg ye. Kãndg tõnd n tʋg sor-tɩrga."
  38,23,"Ad yãoã yaa mam saam-biiga, a tara pe-yãams pis-wae la a wae, tɩ mam tar pe-yãang a ye, la a yeel-yã: ""kõ-a maam tɩ m lok"" . La a wila maam goamã pʋgẽ."
  38,24,"T'a (Dawʋʋd) yeele: ""sɩd la hakɩɩka a wẽga foom ne a sẽn kos fo pe-yãangã n na paas a pe-yãamsã, la tʋmd-n-taarã rãmb wʋsg fãa, sãndã wẽgda sãndã, rẽnda rãmb nins sẽn kõ sɩd la tʋmd sẽn sõmbã, la bãmb rãmb paooda"". La a Dawʋʋd tẽegɑme tɩ Tõnd zarb-a lame n na n gese yel-kãngɑ pʋgẽ, t'a kos yaafa ne a Soabã, n lʋɩ n põond n lebs a meng Wẽnd nengẽ."
  38,25,"Tɩ Tõnd yaaf-a, rẽnd a tara zĩig sẽn zẽk Tõnd nengẽ la lεbeng zĩig sẽn be neere."
  38,26,"Yaa foom Dawʋʋda, Tõnd ninga foom tɩ f yaa lεdsd tẽng zugu, bɩ f bʋ neba ne taab sʋk ne sɩda, la f ra tũ f yõor yamleoog t'a wa menems foom n yi Wẽnd sorã zug ye. Ad neb nins sẽn menemd n yit Wẽnd sorã, b tara naong sẽn keeme b sẽn yĩm Geelgã Raarã yĩngɑ."
  38,27,"La Tõnd pa naan saagã ne tẽngã la bũmb ning sẽn be b yiibã sʋkã zaalem yĩng ye, woto la sẽn kɩfl-bã tẽeda, la wɩɩbd be ne neb nins sẽn kɩflã."
  38,28,"Tõnd na maan sẽn kõ-b sɩd la b tʋm sẽn sõmbã wala sãamdbã tẽngã zugã sɩda? Bɩ Tõnd na maan wẽn-zoetbã wala nin-wẽnsã?."
  38,29,"Yãoã yaa bark gafo tɩ Tõnd sika fo nengẽ, bʋɩl yĩng tɩ b na tags n ges a aaya-rãmbã, la sẽn na yɩlẽ tɩ yam-bεεl rãmbã tẽege."
  38,30,"La Tõnd kõo a Dawʋʋd a Sʋleymaan, ad yaa yamb-sõng tεkẽ! A yiime n ya lebs-m-meng soaba."
  38,31,"Wakat ning b sẽn wa n tedg a nengẽ wed-zoets sẽn be neere, zaabr sasa."
  38,32,"T'a yeele: ""mam bʋʋ arzεka (wiidi wã) nonglem n yɩɩd m Soabã yʋʋr tẽegr hal tɩ wĩngã wa tʋg n lʋɩ."
  38,33,"Lebs-y-b mam nengẽ, t'a saagd b karsã la b yubli wã."
  38,34,"Sɩd la hakɩɩka Tõnd zarba a Sʋleymaan n na n gese, n lobg sʋtãɑn a zaoorẽ wã, t'ɑ mɑɑ-ɑ mengã wɑlɑ ned; n tɑl nɑɑmɑ wɑkɑt bilfu, rẽ poorẽ tɩ nɑɑmɑ lebg n wɑ ɑ nengẽ, tɩ Wẽnd kõ-ɑ pãng zĩnd-dãmbã zugu."
  38,35,"A yeelame: ""yaa m Soaba! yaaf-ma, la f kõ-m naam sẽn pa sõmb ne ned ba a ye mam poorẽ ye, ad Foom la kũun Naaba""."
  38,36,"Tɩ Tõnd nom sebgã n kõ-a t'a zoet bʋg-bʋg ne a sagelle, a sẽn rat zĩig ning fãa."
  38,37,"La Sʋɩtãambã, tɩ b yaa metb la yẽedba."
  38,38,"Tɩ sãnda sẽn wεgmɑ, bãm yaa sẽn sẽb tɩ b lagem taab bãeensã pʋgẽ."
  38,39,"Wãndã yaa Tõnd kũuni, bɩ f kõ ma f gãde, tɩ geelg ka be ye."
  38,40,"La a tara zĩig sẽn zẽk Tõnd nengẽ la lεbeng zĩig sẽn be neere."
  38,41,"La f tẽeg Tõnd yamb a Ayʋʋb yelle, wakat ning a sẽn wa n bool a Soabã n yeele: ''A Sʋɩtãan bolga maam ne yaams la naongo''."
  38,42,"""Tĩng ne f naoorã, tɩ wãndã yaa pekr zĩig sẽn maas la yũubu""."
  38,43,"Tɩ Tõnd kõ-a a nebã, la b buud n lagem-ba, tɩ yaa yolsg sẽn yi Tõnd nengẽ la tags-n-gesg ne yam-bεεl rãmba."
  38,44,"(A sẽn wɑ zɑb ne ɑ pɑgã n wẽen t'ɑ nɑ pã-bɑ sãbg koɑbgã, Tõnd yeel-ɑ lɑme): Yãk mo-kill ne f nugã n pãb ne-a la f ra yidg f wẽenegã ye, lɑ Tõnd mik-a lame t'a yaa sugr soaba, ad yaa yamb-sõng tεkẽ, a ra yɩɩme n ya lebs-n-meng soaba."
  38,45,"La tẽeg Tõnd yembsã a ɭbraahɩɩm la a Ishaaka, la a Yaakuub yelle, sẽn yaa pãng rãmb la pʋ-tẽer-rãmba."
  38,46,"Tõnd welg-b lame ne laahrã tẽegr bala."
  38,47,"La ad Tõnd nengẽ, b bee b sẽn tũus-b rãmbẽ wã sẽn yaa nin-tũusdbã."
  38,48,"La f tẽeg a ɭsmaa-ɩɩl yelle, la a Ya-sa'ɑ, la a Zʋlkɩfl, b gillã been nin-tũusdẽ wã."
  38,49,"Yãoã yaa tẽegre, la ad wẽn-zoetbã tara lεbeng zĩig sẽn be neere."
  38,50,"Arzãn ruumds pʋgẽ, tɩ rag-noe wã yaa sẽn pak bãmb yĩnga."
  38,51,"Tɩ b kɩll a pʋgẽ n boond (tɩ b kõ-b b yam) tɩ-biis wʋsgo, la bõn-yũudi."
  38,52,"B tara ges-koees rãmba, pʋg-neeb sẽn yaa reem-n-taase."
  38,53,"Woto la b pʋlem-ba, Geelgã Raare."
  38,54,"Wãndã yaa tõnd rɩtla, pa tar saab ye."
  38,55,"Yaa woto, la kεdgdbã me tara lεbeng zĩig sẽn ya wẽnga."
  38,56,"Gεhannem tɩ b kẽed-a; gãag zĩig yɩ wẽnga."
  38,57,"Sã n ya woto, bɩ b lemb-a, ko-kaeedg la nod-meto."
  38,58,"La naong kõbg toor-toor sẽn leb n wõnd woto."
  38,59,"Woto yaa zãma sẽn na n sẽdg n kẽ n lagem yãmba, beelg pa be ne-b ye, ad b yaa Bugmã kẽedba."
  38,60,"(Tɩ kɩfr-dãmb ne taab) yeele: ""yãmb zĩig n pa be neer kae, yãmb n kẽes tõnd a pʋgẽ, rẽnd tablg zĩig yɩ wẽnga""."
  38,61,"b yeelame: ""yaa tõnd Soabã! Ned ning sẽn ya-a sabab n wa ne tõnd ka wã, bɩ F rogl-a naong n paas Bugmã pʋgẽ""."
  38,62,"La b yeele: ""yaa bõe tɩ tõnd pa ne roap tõnd sẽn da yɩ n tẽed tɩ b yaa nin-wẽense?''"
  38,63,"Tõnd rɩk-b-la ne yaalg bɩ yaa d ninã n pa ne-ba?"""
  38,64,"Ad Bugum koambã zab-taabã woto wã yaa sɩd tɩ sik kɑbe ye."
  38,65,"Yeele: ""ad mam yaa bugsda, la soab buud kae rẽnda Wẽnde, sẽn yaa Soab-Yεnga, n yaa Modgr Naaba"""
  38,66,"Saas la tẽng Soaba, la bũmb ning sẽn be b yiibã sʋka, n ya wilb Naaba, n ya Yaafg Naaba."
  38,67,"Yeele: ""ad a yaa kɩba-bedre,"
  38,68,"Tɩ yãmb yaa balldb n yita."
  38,69,"Mam ra pa tar ba bãngr ne yĩngr zãmã wã wakat ning b sẽn wa n takd taabã ye."
  38,70,"B pa tʋms tɩ wa mam nengẽ, rallame tɩ mam yaa bugsd sẽn vẽnege."
  38,71,"Wakat ning fo Soabã sẽn wa n yeel Malεgsã: ""Mam na n naana yĩng soaba, ne tãndo,"
  38,72,"La M sã n wa maneg-a la M fʋʋs a pʋgẽ wã Mam vɩɩmã, bɩ y lʋɩ n maan-a suguudu""."
  38,73,"Tɩ malεgsã fãa gill maan-a suguudu."
  38,74,"Ralla a ɭblɩɩs sẽn waoog a menga, n lagem kɩfr-rãmbã."
  38,75,"A yeelame: ""yaa foom a ɭblɩɩsa! Bõe n gɩdg foom tɩ f maan Suguud ne bũmb ning Mam sẽn naan ne M Nus a yiibã, f waooga f meng bɩ f yɩɩme n be zẽk-m-meng rãmbẽ wã?"""
  38,76,"A yeelame (ɭblɩɩs): ""mam são-a lame, Fo naana maam ne bugum, la F naan yẽ ne tãndo""."
  38,77,"T'A (Wẽnd) yeele: "" bɩ f yi [azrãnã pʋga] bala fo yaa b sẽn rig n zãag yolsgo!"
  38,78,"La ad mam kãabg be fo zug n tãag Rolbã Raare""."
  38,79,"T'a yeele: ""yaa m Soaba! koll maam n tɩ tãag raar ning b sẽn nɑ n nek nebã"""
  38,80,"Tɩ [Wẽnd] yeele: ""ad fo naaga b sẽn na n koll-b rãmbã."
  38,81,"Hal n tɩ ta raar Wẽnd sẽn mi."
  38,82,"T'a (ɭblɩɩs) yeele: ""m wẽen ne Fo zɩslemã, la tɩ m na raag-ba, b gilli,"
  38,83,"Sã n pa Fo yembs nins sẽn yaa pʋ-peelem rãmbã""."
  38,84,"T'A (Wẽnd) yeele: ""yaa sɩda! La yaa sɩd bal la Mam yetã,"
  38,85,"La tɩ M na pids Gεhannemã neer-neer ne foom la neb nins sẽn pʋg-b foomã gilli."
  38,86,"Yeele: ""mam pa kot yãmb keoor a zug ye; la m pa yɩ me n yaa rogl-m-mens rãmb b sẽn pa tõe ye""."
  38,87,"A (Alkʋrãanã) pa yɩ rẽnda tẽegr ne bõn-naandsã."
  38,88,"La lak tɩ y na bãng Alkʋrãɑnɑ kɩbarã wakt bilf poor bala."
